title: Australian health experts warn Trump’s unfounded autism claims about paracetamol may harm pregnant women
summary: The TGA has officially deemed a drug safe for use during pregnancy, addressing concerns among doctors about misinformation from the White House. This confirmation aims to reassure both healthcare professionals and pregnant individuals regarding the drug's safety. The situation highlights the ongoing issues surrounding accurate information and public health messaging.

title: Hungary refuses to stop buying Russian oil despite Trump’s Nato demand
summary: The foreign minister expressed skepticism about the feasibility of sourcing energy supplies from alternative locations, calling it a "nice dream."
